# Reverse pyramid

Reverse pyramid is a JavaScript exercise to create a reverse pyramid asking the user to enter the reverse pyramid size.

## Installation

Clone this [project](git@github.com:preciado04/reverse-pyramid.git) to install reverse pyramid.

```bash
git clone git@github.com:preciado04/reverse-pyramid.git
```

Enter to **reverse-pyramid** folder and open index.html file on your browser.

## Usage

Enter the reverse pyramid size and submit the form.

E.g. 5 will print this:
```
* * * * *
 * * * *
  * * *
   * *
    *
```

